track_notes: I parked in the layby across from the Cat & Fiddle Pub. This is a return track.

Parked roadside in small space at junc of A537 and minor road. Walk up road short way and T L into cafe. Straight ahead (N) towards farm. Just before farm cross fence on R and go diagonally up field to meet main path from Cat and Fiddle. Pass through gate and continue N for 180m. Turn L (NW) and follow path down then up to summit.

Total time (including ops): 1hr 50m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Shining Tor Linear from A537. May 2019.
